              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two targets of a nuclide under study, each about 500",
                "mugramm/cm**2, were placed at 45 degree in respect to",
                "the proton beam direction. The targets of indium and",
                "antimony were prepared by vacuum evaporation onto an",
                "Aluminium backing, 150 mugramm/cm**2 thick. The",
                "Targets of silver and tin were self-supporting films.",
                "The targets were made of extra-pure materials.",
                "Presence of heavy fissile admixtures was checked by",
                "activation analysis and by thermal neutron irradiation.",
                "The admixture of uranium was found less than",
                "1*10**(-7) g/g in tin and less than 2.5*10**(-7) g/g",
                "in silver."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FISCT",
                "EXTB",
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GLASD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Silicate glass detectors, 0.5*1.7 cm**2 size,",
                "were placed around every target at 6 cm distance,",
                "covering 20-160 deg. angles with 10 deg. step. The",
                "detectors registered only particles with mass A>=20",
                "and energy more than 13-15 MeV.",
                "Detection efficiency was calculated assuming a",
                "gaussian-shaped energy distribution of fission",
                "fragments in C.M.S., with the FWHM of 30 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "PART-DET": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "FF"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "."
              ]
            }
          ],
