            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-By Compiler- The Reference given under 'MONIT-REF'",
                "contains the cross sections for the reaction given",
                "under 'MONIT' in the energy range 50-160 MeV only.",
                "The data were extrapolated up to 200 MeV by the authors",
